le=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-error-color);\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-name-color);\">next</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-text-color);\">(</span><span class=\"nx\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-name-color);\">err</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-text-color);\">));</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-text-color);\">});</span></code></pre><div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; display: flex; visibility: hidden;\"><div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; padding: var(--su-2); overflow: hidden; background: var(--base-60); border-bottom-left-radius: var(--radius); opacity: 0.9;\">&nbsp;</div></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0;\">Where the bootstrap property is exported like this (it isn't included in the created files that's why there was an issue logged in GitHub about it, someone's bug, is another one's blessing I guess).</p><div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color); font-size: 16px; border-radius: var(--radius); margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; overflow-x: auto; overflow-wrap: initial; padding: var(--su-6); position: relative;\"><pre class=\"highlight typescript\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 1em; background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color); overflow: auto;\"><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0px;\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-comment-color);\">// main.server.ts minimum line</span><span class=\"k\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);\">export</span> <span class=\"k\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);\">default</span> <span class=\"p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-text-color);\">()</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-error-color);\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-name-color);\">bootstrapApplication</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-text-color);\">(</span><span class=\"nx\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-name-color);\">AppComponent</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--syntax-text-color);\">);</span></code></pre><div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; display: flex; visibility: hidden;\"><div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; padding: var(--su-2); overflow: hidden; background: var(--base-60); border-bottom-left-radius: var(--radius); opacity: 0.9;\">&nbsp;</div></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0;\">It may look like using the&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;\">CommonEngine</code>&nbsp;directly is more flexible and gives more options, but knowing that I will have to use that in my&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: